div.div:
Use case by API
IOPS - POST/ Create Payment Session
IOPS - GET/ Payment status as event (by order-number, by IOPG ID,)
IOPS - DELETE / Delete Payment Session
IOPS - PUT / Update Payment Session
Devops
Use case by scenario
1. User initiates a payment on IKEA online payment widget. (CREATE, GET)
2. User modifies the cart after initiating the payment. (DELETE)
3. User initiates a payment using Apple Pay (CREATE, PUT, GET)
4. Devops - Dev deploys the code or configuration to the environment.
